dcterms:description: Mobility and population activity data collected from commercial location intelligence providers, containing anonymized and aggregated data related to population visitations to points of interest (POI) as well as micro-mobility characteristics.
dcterms:title: Mobility and Population Activity Data from Spectus and SafeGraph

dcterms:description: Public health data containing health measures related to obesity, diabetes, cancer, and heart disease collected from the CDC, available at county, place, census tract, and ZIP Code Tabulation Area levels.
dcterms:title: Public Health Data (Obesity, Diabetes, Cancer, Heart Disease)

dcterms:description: PM2.5 emission data provided by the CDC, containing modeled predictions of PM2.5 levels at the census tract level.
dcterms:title: PM2.5 Emission Data

dcterms:description: POI density data collected from SafeGraph, quantifying the number of different types of points of interest in each census tract.
dcterms:title: POI Density Data from SafeGraph

dcterms:description: American Community Survey data retrieved from the US Census Bureau, providing socio-demographic information including age, income, and minority status.
dcterms:title: American Community Survey Data
